
Chip info :  
- Broadcom BCM2711
  = SoC
  + includes an ARM Cortex-A72 CPU
  + GPU
  + VPU
  + mem ifces
  + I/O ifces
  + peris


Memory :
- on-chip ROM : 4MB 
- SDRAM : 1-8 GB of LPDDR4


Interfaces :
- I2C :
  = I2C-0 , I2C-1 , I2C-2 via GPIO w/ a I2C bus 
  + dedicated libs and APIs
- SPI :
  = SPI-0, SPI-1 via GPIO w/ a I2C bus 
- UART : 
  = UART0 , UART1
  + dedicated libs and APIs via a GPIO w/ a UART bus 


Pinout :
- GPIO
- 20 d-pins
- 6 PWM pins
- 6 a-pins 


Volt :
- input : 7-12V
- operating : 5V , USB 






(
- EEPROM 
  - SPI
- flash
  - SPI NAND 
)